---
layout: page.njk
title: City Budget
subtitle: Aberdeen's annual budget documents, financial reports, and transparency resources.
description: City of Aberdeen annual budget documents, financial statements, and public transparency information.
breadcrumb:
  - label: Budget
---

<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
  <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-10">

    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-base">The City of Aberdeen is committed to fiscal transparency. The annual budget is prepared by the City Manager, reviewed by the public, and adopted by the Mayor and City Council. All budget documents are available to residents for review.</p>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-5">Budget Documents</h2>
      <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden divide-y divide-slate-100">
        {% for doc in [
          { label: "FY2026 Adopted Budget", sub: "Current fiscal year", url: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/finance/pages/budgets" },
          { label: "Where Does Your Money Go? (FY2026)", sub: "Plain-language budget summary", url: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/finance/files/where-does-your-money-go-fy2026-0" },
          { label: "FY2025 Budget", sub: "Prior fiscal year", url: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/finance/pages/budgets" },
          { label: "All Budget Archives", sub: "Past fiscal years", url: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/finance/pages/budgets" }
        ] %}
        <a href="{{ doc.url }}" class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 px-5 py-4 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors duration-150 group">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gov-blue-light flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:bg-gov-blue transition-colors duration-150">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-4 h-4 text-gov-blue group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 4a2 2 0 012-2h4.586A2 2 0 0112 2.586L15.414 6A2 2 0 0116 7.414V16a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V4zm2 6a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 110 2H7a1 1 0 01-1-1zm1 3a1 1 0 100 2h6a1 1 0 100-2H7z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-navy group-hover:text-gov-blue transition-colors duration-150">{{ doc.label }}</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5">{{ doc.sub }}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400 group-hover:text-gov-blue flex-shrink-0 transition-colors duration-150" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-5">Budget Process</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        {% for step in [
          { n: "1", title: "City Manager Prepares", desc: "The City Manager develops the proposed budget based on departmental needs and City Council priorities." },
          { n: "2", title: "Public Comment Period", desc: "Residents have the opportunity to review and comment on the proposed budget at public sessions." },
          { n: "3", title: "City Council Review", desc: "The Mayor and City Council hold work sessions to review and amend the proposed budget." },
          { n: "4", title: "Adoption", desc: "The City Council formally adopts the annual budget, typically before the start of the fiscal year on July 1." }
        ] %}
        <div class="flex gap-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gov-blue text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">{{ step.n }}</div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-bold text-navy mb-1">{{ step.title }}</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">{{ step.desc }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gov-blue-light rounded-xl p-6">
      <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-navy mb-2">Weekly Activity Reports</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">The City Manager's office publishes weekly reports summarizing city expenditures and operations — a great way to stay informed about how the City uses public resources.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/home/pages/2026-weekly-activity-reports" class="text-sm text-gov-blue font-semibold hover:underline">2026 Reports</a>
        <a href="https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/home/pages/2025-weekly-activity-reports" class="text-sm text-gov-blue font-semibold hover:underline">2025 Reports</a>
        <a href="https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/home/pages/2024-city-hall-weekly-activity-reports" class="text-sm text-gov-blue font-semibold hover:underline">2024 Reports</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <aside>
    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6 sticky top-24 space-y-5">
      <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-navy pb-3 border-b border-slate-100">Finance Department</h2>
      <dl class="space-y-4 text-sm">
        <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Phone</dt><dd><a href="tel:+14102721600" class="text-gov-blue hover:underline">(410) 272-1600 ext. 200</a></dd></div>
        <div><dt class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Hours</dt><dd class="text-slate-700">Mon–Fri, 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM</dd></div>
      </dl>
      <div class="pt-2 space-y-2">
        <a href="{{ '/services/taxes/' | url }}" class="block w-full text-center bg-gov-blue text-white text-sm font-semibold py-2.5 rounded hover:bg-gov-blue-dark transition-colors duration-200">Property Tax Info</a>
        <a href="{{ '/services/pay-bills/' | url }}" class="block w-full text-center border border-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-sm font-semibold py-2.5 rounded hover:border-gov-blue hover:text-gov-blue transition-colors duration-200">Pay Bills Online</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>
